30,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"素食撚又話黃豆同豆腐仲高鈣過肉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:26:56.000Z","msg":"黃豆同豆腐真係好比高鈣過肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e0c411e530acb619f09f34cfac387668eca5e8","tid":1141130,"uid":113373,"like":32,"dislike":9,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n星期六 早上9點 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">事態危急</span><br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dedbc29bd4350ffcfd6b6c66aea6a2fee68f3ead","tid":1141130,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:32:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>素食撚又話黃豆同豆腐仲高鈣過肉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>黃豆同豆腐真係好比高鈣過肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsor打錯<br />\n係鐵質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有波菜好似都高鐵質"},{"pid":"b7f81ea89efae623c362ebfa7780306006aa60f0","tid":1141130,"uid":141869,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"99c6956187f9c8b7ea51fa2e87ae30f81d9d5481","tid":1141130,"uid":216538,"like":106,"dislike":7,"score":99,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:05:50.000Z","msg":"淨係食素本身就係一種揀飲雜食，係唔健康的飲食習慣<br />\n<br />\n你想揀飲雜食到健康？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/06/180548_0275d4669989901370ef9a18534ce737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F06%2F180548_0275d4669989901370ef9a18534ce737.jpg&h=a1cca8d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:37:29.000Z","msg":"㨂飲<span style=\"color: red;\">擇</span>食"},{"pid":"a6de792987485f474c75a7a2cabf5091eab104d6","tid":1141130,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"奶下個鐵鑊就得<br />\n冇咩問題"},{"pid":"c5fde9eaeb8bf226beef09f927d5493068c8ee7b","tid":1141130,"uid":120034,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"a714162133b692b7285fbbe2d51dcdb33231efec","tid":1141130,"uid":63575,"like":347,"dislike":2,"score":345,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T09:59:05.000Z","msg":"第一句係真嘅，日本都有研究出過話日本人近呢幾十年鐵質低下，除咗食物之物，其中一個方法就係用返鑄鐵類煮食用具，或者落鐵魚煲湯。鐵魚係東南亞或者一啲再舊啲嘅發展中國家係好重要，因為佢地好大機會長期營養不良，鐵魚成本低而又可以輕鬆解決鐵質吸收問題。<br />\n<br />\n當然呢啲鐵質同動物性鐵質無得比，但係好過無。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:45:50.000Z","msg":"同埋以前既航海員係會用檸檬汁浸鐵釘黎飲"},{"pid":"2e802ec5deadc475174e136589148037b49966fc","tid":1141130,"uid":36995,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:58:19.000Z","msg":"又稱雲耳的黑木耳，每100克煮熟黑木耳，含46毫克鐵質，為食物中的鐵質之王。 黑豆、芝麻也是鐵質非常豐富的食物，一向標榜可「補鐵」的菠菜，其鐵質含量則比上述食物低。"},{"pid":"fafb1b09d1ab3e14f1d092d10fe096b3e1706d6f","tid":1141130,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:01:59.000Z","msg":"原來真係work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ac806aaa40ba7682c297e5f8adad5453bf8e9f","tid":1141130,"uid":162177,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6HBBJ37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6HBBJ37.jpg&h=a2744147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DpaKSXt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDpaKSXt.jpg&h=42724f35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f5888f1c35695b8b8030e3243a